articles.title: The colloidal stability of albumin-based drug delivery systems has a profound effect on tumoricidal activity.
articles.summary: Researchers developed a modified albumin nanoparticle drug delivery system with improved colloidal stability, resulting in better paclitaxel tumor targeting and antitumor efficacy compared to Abraxane.
